lled on your system.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":13,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":14,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"### Installation Steps","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":15,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"1. Download the latest `.jar` release file of CareContacts.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":16,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"2. Move the downloaded `.jar` file into an empty folder in your computer.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":17,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"3. Open a terminal or command prompt in that folder.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":18,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"4. Run the following command:","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":19,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"```java -jar *.jar```","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":20,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":21,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"The application should launch in a new window.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":22,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":23,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"## Features","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":24,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"### 1. Add a Student","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":25,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"Adds a new student and their associated parent details to the address book.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":26,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"### 2. Delete a Student","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":27,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"Removes a student and all associated information from the address book.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":28,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"### 3. List All Students","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":29,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"Displays all students and their associated information.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":30,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"### 4. Help","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":31,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"Displays available commands and their formats.","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":32,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":33,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"## Acknowledgements","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":34,"author":{"gitId":"Annazx"},"content":"This project is based on the AddressBook-Level3 project created by the [SE-EDU initiative](https://se-education.org).","lastModifiedDate":"2026-03-04T19:23:40","isFullCredit":false}],"authorContributionMap":{"kah-seng":2,"Annazx":30,"-":2}},{"path":"docs/AboutUs.md","fileType":"docs","lines":[{"lineNumber":1,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"---","lastModifiedDate":"2020-05-23T01:10:16","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":2,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"  layout: default.md","lastModifiedDate":"2023-09-12T01:20:47","isFullCredit":false},{"lineNumber":3,"author":{"gitId":"-"},"content":"  title: \"About Us\"","lastModifiedDate":"2023-09-12T01:20:47",